<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">

<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Kursy</title>

<style>

body{
    background:#050505;
    color:white;
    font-family:Arial;
    margin:0;
}

h1{
    text-align:center;
    margin-top:50px;
    font-size:70px;
}

.green{
    color:#39ff14;
}

.container{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:40px;
    margin-top:80px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.card{
    background:#111;
    width:400px;
    border-radius:25px;
    overflow:hidden;
    transition:0.3s;
    text-align:center;
    padding-bottom:30px;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(57,255,20,0.3);
}

.card img{
    width:100%;
    height:320px;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.card h2{
    margin-top:25px;
    color:#39ff14;
}

.card p{
    color:#cfcfcf;
    padding:20px;
    line-height:1.6;
}

.card a{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:15px 30px;
    background:#39ff14;
    color:black;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:15px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>
Nasze <span class="green">Kursy</span>
</h1>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<img src="Kukirin-G4-elektricni-skiro-promo4.webp">

<h2>Kurs KuKirin G4</h2>

<p>
Poznaj wszystko o KuKirin G4,
serwisie i osiągach.
</p>

<a href="kurs1.html">
Wejdź
</a>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="Kukirin-G4-elektricni-skiro-promo4.webp">

<h2>Serwis i Tuning</h2>

<p>
Zaawansowany kurs tuningu
i napraw hulajnóg.
</p>

<a href="kurs2.html">
Wejdź
</a>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
